intro.tooling.head: Tooling
intro.tooling.content:
This project is served and bundled with $t(intro.tooling.link, { 'item': 'Vite' }). If you need to test your components and web pages, check out $t(intro.tooling.link, { 'item': 'Cypress' }) and $t(intro.tooling.link, { 'item': 'Cypress Component Testing' }).

intro.echosystem.head: Ecosystem
intro.echosystem.content:
Get official tools and libraries for your project: Pinia, Vue Router, Vue Test Utils, and Vue Dev Tools.
If you need more resources, we suggest paying Awesome Vue a visit.
